column5: With the nearing of the holiday season some may find it prudent to watch these informative videos on the consequences of excessive consumption.    NO NO not me- I dont do that..       Come to think of it I may have experienced a good many of those side effects.
... and that is exactly why I don't allow cameras around when i'm gettin' poop-faced!!!
Ahhh, to be invisible again  Those were funny, thanks.  Joey
DANG !!!  I didn't know they were taken my picture...  talk about "REMEMBER WHEN"...
